        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="806052861">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-806052861" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-806052861" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="806052861">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ryo-/">困扁头</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-05-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一套全三册读毕 嘛 通俗读物 语言风格很轻快很幽默 能短期内对于IJN从崛起到凋谢的过程有个大体的认识</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="818921559">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-818921559" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-818921559" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="818921559">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/perseusfy/">羊</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-08-19</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">书很好，不过总感觉有点凌乱，好像作者想到哪写到哪似的，另外，还有年代和人名上的错误。总体来说很好。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1076661755">
